and not margarine, the first one that we will prepare it is one of fine herbs which I think

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:08.340
it is the most common and has multiple uses, what we will need is butter a

00:01:08.340 --> 00:01:14.320
room temperature, salt to taste, 1/4 cup of basil, a clove of garlic, parsley,

00:01:14.580 --> 00:01:20.800
dill and rosemary. The first thing we are going to do it is put the butter in the bowl and add

00:01:20.800 --> 00:01:26.760
