00:01:43.260 --> 00:01:48.260
that you like, for example chives or tarragon. When you see that everything is perfectly

00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:53.720
mixed, you will take cling paper, stretch it very well and in the center you will place the butter

00:01:53.720 --> 00:01:59.160
prepared. Then you will cover it and entangle it in this way to give it this kind of shape

00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:04.430
