00:02:15.970 --> 00:02:21.840
next preparation it is a garlic one. For this, we will need 2 tablespoons of garlic powder, you can replace it

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:26.900
for 2 cloves of minced garlic, remember that the herbs can be fresh or dried,

00:02:26.900 --> 00:02:32.320
a little fresh scallion, basil, remember that herbs can be fresh or dried.

00:02:41.200 --> 00:02:46.800
