00:02:52.190 --> 00:02:54.480
to prepare grilled chicken or sauces

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:59.520
4th preparation it is a chipotle  (smoked hot chilli pepper used in Mexican cooking.), you are going to use 4 tablespoons

