00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:57.980
a butter of flavor. So you know, if you have any favorite salsa, use it

00:03:57.980 --> 00:04:02.709
and make butter. And these are the 4 recipes of salty butters, now I will teach you

00:04:02.709 --> 00:04:08.220
to prepare 5 types of sweet butters. For the 1st we will do is one of strawberries

00:04:08.220 --> 00:04:14.740
natural You will need half a cup of clean and dry strawberries. if strawberries are a little watery

00:04:14.740 --> 00:04:20.480
It will be much better, teaspoons of sugar and 150g of butter at room temperature.

00:04:20.620 --> 00:04:26.000
For this, cut the strawberry into small pieces and put it in the blender or

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:30.900
in a food processor to mix it perfectly and wrap it in vitafilm paper.

00:04:32.240 --> 00:04:38.980
The 2nd preparation is a mango one, I love it! For this, I will use mango jam, in which I will have to

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:43.100
use 2 tablespoons and I will also put natural mango, because I want to feel

00:04:43.100 --> 00:04:47.700
mango bits. Put them in blender and wrap it in cling paper, with this recipe,

00:04:47.700 --> 00:04:51.530
you give yourself idea that you can prepare fruit butter of any flavor. You can also

00:04:51.530 --> 00:04:55.930
use your favorite jam, even if, do not use sugar because jam

00:04:55.930 --> 00:04:56.680
has sugar

00:04:57.720 --> 00:05:02.240
The 3rd preparation it is of lemon. What you will need it is a trickle of vanilla

00:05:02.250 --> 00:05:08.000
and a fresh lemon. You will put everything in a bowl and you will add juice of half of

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:13.090
a lemon, to add aroma we will put the vanilla and zest of the same lemon.

00:05:13.090 --> 00:05:17.130
Mix it very well with a balloon type beater (remember that butter should be

00:05:17.130 --> 00:05:21.380
at room temperature) to make it easier to mix all the ingredients.

00:05:22.420 --> 00:05:27.900
The last preparation it will be sweet spices, you'll need a teaspoon of cinnamon powder, a pinch

00:05:27.900 --> 00:05:32.780
of cloves, half a teaspoon of nutmeg. Mix all powders perfectly

00:05:32.780 --> 00:05:38.420
and add them to your butter, beat very well until there is a homogeneous mixture and wrap it,

00:05:38.580 --> 00:05:42.920
You can use this butter when you prepare pancakes or cakes, you will see that they will have

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:47.880
a unique and delicious flavor. All these sweet butters recipes, you can use them

00:05:47.889 --> 00:05:52.990
for your hot cakes, waffles, for when you only crave a slice of bread with milk,

00:05:52.990 --> 00:05:57.710
